Deciding the margins

@page {
	margin-top:7cm;
	margin-bottom:2cm;
}

@page:left {
	margin-top:7cm;
	margin-bottom:2cm;
	margin-left:2cm;
	margin-right:3cm;
}

@page:left {
	margin-top:7cm;
	margin-bottom:2cm;
	margin-left:3cm;
	margin-right:2cm;
}

@media print {
	
}

page-break-after

puts a page break before the chapter. 

div.chapter {
	page-break-before: always;
}

basically avoid page breaks in running text

p {
	page-break-inside:avoid;
}